episode: I have too many feelings that I shouldn't be having in the first place

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: My feelings are disgusting and I shouldn't be having them in the first place.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: What's going on that's making you feel that way?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Just my feelings for others. It's pathetic.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Having strong feelings for someone can be overwhelming.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It's disgusting, is what it is.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It sounds like you're really struggling with these emotions.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I don't want to have these feelings anymore

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It can be painful to feel things you wish you didn't.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: And I don't anymore.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: So you've been able to let go of them?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: No.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It's still a struggle then.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Yes, obviously, why would it not be one?

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: I can sense the frustration and helplessness.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Oh, you can sense it, huh?

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Your words convey a lot of emotion.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: This is mucho unhelpful.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: I'm sorry if I'm not providing the support you need.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Goodbye.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Take care of yourself.
